subject: Golf
PGA Championship
lead_paragraph: Holmes and Dustin Johnson had a hole in one on the par-3 fourth, but Holmes also strung together four consecutive birdies on the back nine to stay atop the Cadillac Championship leaderboard for the third straight round.
